Package aom.scripting.xs.rm

Class RandomMap

Object
RandomMap
public abstract class RandomMap
extends Object
This class provides a collection of RM commands that don't fit in any of the subcategories. Credits to HyenaStudio's (and M0nTy_PyTh0n in particular) for most of the documentation.
Author:
Mythic_Freak - mythic.freak[a]gmail.com
Local Call
[@local RMS commands are always executed locally. If all players have the same map script, and the same seed is used, the result should be the same for all players.]
See Also:
Hyena Studio's
